{"tid":1045860,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔明","createTime":"2019-03-03T21:44:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T22:24:01.000Z","uid":122766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ccc094589f0408d02d61089ed58ebc563b762971","tid":1045860,"uid":122766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T21:44:34.000Z","msg":"無論有無人覆都好.. 我想發洩情緒姐<br />\n<br />\n同佢一齊左兩年 開始越來越唔想搞 係佢唔想搞我..<br />\n明明硬左都拒絕我 一至五佢話返工翻黎好眼訓，ok 可以 禮拜六日佢寧願繼續訓一日都唔搞。未結婚已經好似結婚4年咁 一個月一到三次.. 有三次都偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問佢咩事 係咪我嘅問題 佢話唔係 只係覺得我patpat好暖 貼埋黎好舒服 其他原因佢都唸唔到講唔出...... <br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔想再問再開口 好傷自尊心 搞到自己好似禽獸 <br />\n<br />\n只係真心唔明"},{"pid":"f6a97724e89d8ce7bfdc51046b3f80613add4dfc","tid":1045860,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T21:56:33.000Z","msg":"明唔明又點 到頭來咪又係咁"},{"pid":"a09a2129ba1318b0a2670f6b18e796d1977d500b","tid":1045860,"uid":122766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6a97724e89d8ce7bfdc51046b3f80613add4dfc","tid":1045860,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T21:56:33.000Z","msg":"明唔明又點 到頭來咪又係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T22:01:37.000Z","msg":"起碼都可以知道原因掛.."},{"pid":"bf14f5783575e48fd2b1a95b13863f